						<p>Slab set up near the Śiva temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Ānanda, Mārgaśira ba. 8.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record some gift to the potters by the village officials <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> Reḍḍis and Karaṇams. In characters of about the 17th century A.D.</p>						

